<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 00:32:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列人质的家人在内塔尼亚胡家前举行逾越节家宴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-hold-passover-seder-in-front-of-netanyahus-home/0000018f-06fd-d6a0-a9ef-c6fd1eb30000</link><description>逾越节前夕，数百人呼吁释放凯撒利亚的人质。一名亲戚向内塔尼亚胡呼喊，“在自由的节日里，有 133 名犹太公民被哈马斯囚禁，释放我们，这样我们就能有一位勇敢的领导人来达成协议”</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-hold-passover-seder-in-front-of-netanyahus-home/0000018f-06fd-d6a0-a9ef-c6fd1eb30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军情报主管因 10 月 7 日的失败而辞职，这对其他以色列国防领导人来说变成了沙漏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/resignation-of-idf-intel-chief-over-oct-7-turns-hourglass-for-other-defense-leaders/0000018f-06a0-d682-afcf-16a7bdf10000</link><description>阿哈龙·哈利瓦是哈马斯大屠杀后下台的最高级官员，他无法预测他继续担任以色列军队情报部门负责人会造成多么严重的内部危机，也无法预测他会成为右翼分子的目标极端分子</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/resignation-of-idf-intel-chief-over-oct-7-turns-hourglass-for-other-defense-leaders/0000018f-06a0-d682-afcf-16a7bdf10000</guid></item><item><title>美国不应该制裁一个流氓营，而应该关注内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-sanctioning-a-rogue-battalion-the-u-s-should-focus-on-netanyahus-government/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f68d90000</link><description>如果谴责极端正统的内扎·耶胡达以色列国防军营的“莱希法”涉及约旦河西岸的侵犯人权行为，那么以色列的整个政治梯队都需要承担责任。美国应该明确地说</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-sanctioning-a-rogue-battalion-the-u-s-should-focus-on-netanyahus-government/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f68d90000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查发现，不到四分之一的以色列犹太人支持在加沙重建定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/less-than-quarter-of-israeli-jews-in-favor-of-renewed-settlement-in-gaza-poll-finds/0000018f-0587-d64a-a9af-85efc6e30000</link><description>以色列民主研究所进行的民意调查显示，多数以色列人认为应将加沙控制权交给国际部队，13%的人认为巴勒斯坦权力机构应承担责任</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/less-than-quarter-of-israeli-jews-in-favor-of-renewed-settlement-in-gaza-poll-finds/0000018f-0587-d64a-a9af-85efc6e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸难民营的行动造成大规模破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-operation-in-west-bank-refugee-camp-leaves-massive-destruction-in-its-wake/0000018f-0549-db42-a99f-adfff02c0000</link><description>图尔卡姆附近难民营持续两天的战斗导致房屋墙壁坑坑洼洼，污水漫溢到街道上，电力也时断时续。 “这里发生的事情让我想起了 1948 年，”营地居民说道</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:55:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-operation-in-west-bank-refugee-camp-leaves-massive-destruction-in-its-wake/0000018f-0549-db42-a99f-adfff02c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事情报局长因导致 10 月 7 日袭击事件失败而辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-intelligence-chief-resigns-citing-failures-leading-up-to-oct-7-attack/0000018f-0509-db32-a58f-fdaf20b00000</link><description>阿哈龙·哈利瓦少将是第一位因哈马斯屠杀事件而辞职的以色列高级国防官员。他在辞职信中写道：“我将永远背负着战争的可怕负担”</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-intelligence-chief-resigns-citing-failures-leading-up-to-oct-7-attack/0000018f-0509-db32-a58f-fdaf20b00000</guid></item><item><title>受美国制裁的本·格维尔极右翼顾问试图获取天然气，发现信用卡被冻结</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ben-gvir-advisor-sanctioned-by-u-s-tries-to-get-gas-finds-credit-card-blocked/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f80130000</link><description>周末，本茨·戈普斯坦（Bentzi Gopstein）及其领导的极右组织被列入拜登政府受制裁的极端分子名单。发卡机构CAL表示，发卡公司必须遵守与其相关的法律并采取相应行动</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:16:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ben-gvir-advisor-sanctioned-by-u-s-tries-to-get-gas-finds-credit-card-blocked/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f80130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列自10月7日以来发生的10场自残瘟疫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/this-passover-remember-israels-10-self-inflicted-plagues-since-october-7/0000018f-00d0-d6a0-a9ef-c0dce9dd0000</link><description>从“无战略的瘟疫”到“全面胜利的瘟疫”，自从六个多月前与哈马斯的战争开始以来，以色列领导人给他们的人民带来了一场又一场的瘟疫，而且还看不到结束的迹象</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:39:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/this-passover-remember-israels-10-self-inflicted-plagues-since-october-7/0000018f-00d0-d6a0-a9ef-c0dce9dd0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷发生汽车冲撞和枪击未遂事件，三人受轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/three-people-lightly-wounded-in-car-ramming-attempted-shooting-in-jerusalem/0000018f-04cb-d6a0-a9ef-c4dfa95d0000</link><description>袭击者试图向行人开枪但失败后逃离现场，并在袭击现场附近的一家商店藏身时被捕</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/three-people-lightly-wounded-in-car-ramming-attempted-shooting-in-jerusalem/0000018f-04cb-d6a0-a9ef-c4dfa95d0000</guid></item><item><title>逾越节后，以色列面临选择：人质还是战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/after-passover-israel-will-have-to-choose-hostages-or-war/0000018f-0209-d6a0-a9ef-c29dc3490000</link><description>以色列目前的战略陷阱在各个方面都很明显：伊朗、黎巴嫩和加沙。 ■ 随着人质在囚禁中腐烂，政客们对其家人的求救声表现出冷漠甚至敌意。 ■ 以色列国防军高级军官会因为 10 月 7 日的失败而开始辞职吗？ ■ 拜登政府现在正瞄准内塔尼亚胡的核心弱点</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/after-passover-israel-will-have-to-choose-hostages-or-war/0000018f-0209-d6a0-a9ef-c29dc3490000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：内塔尼亚胡集团获得51个席位，甘茨留在战时联盟，领先优势缩小</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/poll-netanyahu-bloc-gets-51-seats-gantzs-lead-narrows-as-he-stays-in-wartime-coalition/0000018f-03a6-d224-a9cf-07f732b40000</link><description>该调查还探讨了这样一种情况：纳夫塔利·贝内特、摩萨德前局长约西·科恩和吉迪恩·萨尔联合成一个右翼名单，而前以色列国防军副局长亚尔·戈兰则领导工党和梅雷茨之间的左翼联盟</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:55:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/poll-netanyahu-bloc-gets-51-seats-gantzs-lead-narrows-as-he-stays-in-wartime-coalition/0000018f-03a6-d224-a9cf-07f732b40000</guid></item><item><title>真主党声称对以色列北部发射的火箭弹负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article-live/israel-hamas-war-day-199/0000018f-0383-d224-a9cf-07f3f43a0000</link><description>逾越节前夕，人质家属在内塔尼亚胡家门前举行“抗议家宴” ■ 以色列空军在向北部发射火箭弹后袭击黎巴嫩真主党目标 ■ 欧盟扩大对伊朗制裁 ■ 以色列国防军情报局长于 10 月 7 日辞职 ■ 国防部长加兰特在有报道称美国打算制裁极端正统派营后，支持该营 ■ 两名嫌疑人因耶路撒冷汽车撞击袭击事件被捕，造成三人轻伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:16:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article-live/israel-hamas-war-day-199/0000018f-0383-d224-a9cf-07f3f43a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼议员不会因涉嫌袭击被拘留的贝都因人而面临指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-lawmaker-wont-face-charges-on-alleged-assault-on-detained-bedouins/0000018f-0278-db32-a58f-feff0e4b0000</link><description>来自本-格维尔党的议会议员阿尔蒙·科恩 (Almong Cohen) 在 1 月份就 2013 年发生的一起事件接受质询，据称，当时约有 12 名警察殴打了三名以色列贝都因嫌疑人。检方以无罪为由下令结案。科恩：“我不会为任何事情道歉”</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 21:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-lawmaker-wont-face-charges-on-alleged-assault-on-detained-bedouins/0000018f-0278-db32-a58f-feff0e4b0000</guid></item><item><title>人质交易谈判处于危机模式，以色列希望利雅得能够提供帮助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-talks-are-in-crisis-mode-and-israel-is-hoping-that-riyadh-can-help/0000018f-0219-d64a-a9af-86fb25350000</link><description>以色列战时内阁继续寻求解决与哈马斯谈判僵局的方案 ■ 与沙特阿拉伯达成协议可能会达成释放人质的协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 19:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-talks-are-in-crisis-mode-and-israel-is-hoping-that-riyadh-can-help/0000018f-0219-d64a-a9af-86fb25350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长批准政府就正统派法律草案聘请独立顾问的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-approves-govt-request-for-independent-counsel-on-haredi-draft-law/0000018f-01dc-d64a-a9af-85ffa1aa0000</link><description>总检察长加利·巴哈拉夫·米亚拉 (Gali Baharav-Miara) 表示，她无法在法庭上捍卫政府的立场，即极端正统派以色列人应免除以色列国防军服役</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 18:50:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-approves-govt-request-for-independent-counsel-on-haredi-draft-law/0000018f-01dc-d64a-a9af-85ffa1aa0000</guid></item><item><title>从以色列到伊朗：全球武器贸易报告中缺失的数据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-world-doesnt-knows-the-full-scope-of-the-global-arms-trade/0000018f-0023-db32-a58f-fca7bccd0000</link><description>世界各地的决策者和媒体将瑞典智库 SIPRI 的年度报告视为全球武器贸易全面、可靠的信息来源。然而，它提供的数据有太多漏洞</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 18:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-world-doesnt-knows-the-full-scope-of-the-global-arms-trade/0000018f-0023-db32-a58f-fca7bccd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国官员表示，由于本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇的行为而实施新制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-u-s-officials-say-new-sanctions-due-to-conduct-of-ben-gvir-smotrich/0000018f-018b-d6a0-a9ef-c19f11020000</link><description>一位美国消息人士称，极右翼部长本身也被考虑实施制裁，但白宫担心双边关系受到影响。一些美国人士反对使用“制裁”一词，并表示美国只是让以色列遵守其对所有受援国的标准</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 18:13:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-u-s-officials-say-new-sanctions-due-to-conduct-of-ben-gvir-smotrich/0000018f-018b-d6a0-a9ef-c19f11020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将得到援助，但其在华盛顿的地位从未如此动摇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-21/ty-article/.highlight/israel-will-get-its-aid-but-its-standing-in-washington-has-never-been-shakier/0000018f-01ac-db32-a58f-fdaf995f0000</link><description>在以色列历史上最严重的生存危机中，投票反对向以色列提供紧急军事援助，这发出了一个不可否认的信息，表明以色列在民主党中的地位。共和党人不应该声称这次投票证明他们是无可争议的“亲以色列”政党</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:46:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-21/ty-article/.highlight/israel-will-get-its-aid-but-its-standing-in-washington-has-never-been-shakier/0000018f-01ac-db32-a58f-fdaf995f0000</guid></item><item><title>谁写了逾越节哈加达？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/who-wrote-the-haggadah/0000017f-e145-d7b2-a77f-e3474e270000</link><description>不同的人在不同的时间写下了不同的部分，例如，当犹太人避免牺牲时，古代的“四个问题”就发生了变化。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/who-wrote-the-haggadah/0000017f-e145-d7b2-a77f-e3474e270000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官在周三对北部的无人机和导弹袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/idf-officer-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-wednesdays-drone-and-missile-attack-on-north/0000018f-018e-db32-a58f-fdaff0a70000</link><description>27 岁的 Dor Zimel 在真主党袭击阿拉伯基地时受伤 ■ 另有 17 名以色列人在事件中受伤，其中包括 13 名以色列国防军预备役军人</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:10:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/idf-officer-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-wednesdays-drone-and-missile-attack-on-north/0000018f-018e-db32-a58f-fdaff0a70000</guid></item></channel></rss>